  "delivery_domain": "book_authoring",
  "target_brief": "Create an OPL-compatible book authoring Foundry Agent that turns source material into a coherent book. The workflow starts with storyline architecture, then enters chapter production planning directly before chapter materialization, source/style integrity review, and publication proof handoff. The agent must preserve content consistency, writing style consistency, evidence grounding, affirmative human prose, illustration and table planning, proof/export boundary checks, and owner-gated publication decisions.",
